    "Still, they are limited by complex genetic background variations, differences in treatment histories, and, most importantly, the lack of suitable controls 14.",
    "Most importantly, the tumor growth characteristics identified in PDX models were found to be more dependent on the mouse strain than tumor type 15, suggesting the PDX model may generate many artificial readouts irrelevant to primary human tumors.",
